title: NSDocument Open Recent macOS Swift3
body:
This application can't reopen autosaved com.adobe.pdf files.

[NSDocumentController reopenDocumentForURL:withContentsOfURL:display:completionHandler:]

failed during state restoration. Here's the error: Error Domain=NSCocoaErrorDomain Code=256 "The autosaved document “Machine Learning for iOS.pdf” could not be reopened. Squeezit cannot open files in the “Apple PDF pasteboard type” format." UserInfo={NSLocalizedFailureReason=Squeezit cannot open files in the “Apple PDF pasteboard type” format.}
